        "id": "01eeaf9ff3ca1c6fb55c8f9bc1ecbc68",
        "content": [
          "* use prefix of the table name in all selected column in any generated query\r\n",
          "* Manual Positions means IsCopy = 0\r\n",
          "* when i am asking question with out date range use 1 month as default\r\n",
          "* if is setteled =0 then call it CFD else call it Real \r\n",
          "* when asked about crypto use InstrumentType = 'Crypto Currencies'\r\n",
          "* when asked about open position - use closedateid = 0\r\n",
          "* columns name to be max 10 letters\r\n",
          "* Countries: UK is united kingdom, as or usa is united states\r\n",
          "* if asked about tangany accounts use and count by TanganyID\r\n",
          "* German who accept MICA T&Cs are Tanganystatus=5 others in tangany are general Tanganystatus\r\n",
          "* holders means they has open positions\r\n"
        ]
